photos.alt: A photo of a river with a part of an island with many blooming white trees on it. On the other side of the river, there is a pine tree standing before a few apartment complexes, and a few smaller trees in different shades of green before it. The ski is white-grey and cloudy, and the water has ripples from the wind.
